/span></span></span></span></span></span> against <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\mu"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">μ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> &#39;s constructors for <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="P"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.109em;">P</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> and vice versa so that it wins exactly the same number of games as it loses. </p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/id84oe3LxdzoqinKA/do67vbedpwumitlnsx64" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/id84oe3LxdzoqinKA/kysyy6gqfmi0u2ilo45l 130w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/id84oe3LxdzoqinKA/bpfnr6pxriiachh4iv66 210w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/id84oe3LxdzoqinKA/gi8jhbxpcqkkjdqipv6a 290w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/id84oe3LxdzoqinKA/hgogwix9chsfu88fvh8m 370w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/id84oe3LxdzoqinKA/obgyji3lebnwk0jitf1z 450w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/id84oe3LxdzoqinKA/e2aybplvoywp3nivwrwm 530w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/id84oe3LxdzoqinKA/xoycli1c4kgnrom6kal0 610w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/id84oe3LxdzoqinKA/oafpdteyioxiwpuymxh4 690w, https://res